gimme_an_adj_phrase
  1. If you do this:                                                      

     "/areas/Misc/Bad/c/Objects/generic_randomizer"->gimme_an_adj_phrase();  
     "/areas/Misc/Bad/c/Objects/generic_randomizer"->gimme_an_adj_phrase(0); 

     it will return: "A <adjective>"                                    

  1. If you do this:                                                      

     "/areas/Misc/Bad/c/Objects/generic_randomizer"->gimme_an_adj_phrase(1); 

     it will return: "An <adjective>"                                   

